            <title>[DERBY-4937] Enable explicit mode istat daemon code for UPDATE_STATISTICS</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/DERBY-4937</link>
                <project id="10594" key="DERBY">Derby</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Implement SYSCS_UTIL.UPDATE_STATISTICS by having the ALTER TABLE code use the new istat daemon in explicit mode.&lt;br/&gt;
Doing this will allow for a period of limited exposure before the background mode of the daemon is enabled, and it will verify that the code generating the index statistics is working.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
