                            <comment id="12969301" author="kristwaa" created="Wed, 8 Dec 2010 13:33:03 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Attached patch 1a, which makes SYS_CS.UPDATE_STATISTICS, and thus also ALTER TABLE, use the explicit mode daemon code to generate new statistics.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="12969302" author="kristwaa" created="Wed, 8 Dec 2010 13:34:12 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;This patch is blocked by, or dependent on, &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/DERBY-4936&quot; title=&quot;Add core istat daemon&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;DERBY-4936&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;DERBY-4936&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="12970216" author="kristwaa" created="Fri, 10 Dec 2010 16:24:15 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Attaching patch 1b (formatting change only).&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;If you apply this patch now, calls to SYS_CS.UPDATE_STATISTICS will use the new daemon code committed in &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/DERBY-4936&quot; title=&quot;Add core istat daemon&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;DERBY-4936&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;DERBY-4936&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="12976711" author="kristwaa" created="Mon, 3 Jan 2011 12:11:37 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Committed to trunk with revision 1054588.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Any new test failures in tests running UPDATE_STATISTICS is likely to have been caused by this commit.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
